span.span: Allows hosts to programmatically remove [<Import>](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/3bfecaf1-69fd-4008-b651-c9dafd4389d9) tags that are part of a project file being manipulated by the host.

remarks.format: ## Remarks Suppression d’une importation marque le projet comme modifié, ce qui signifie que le projet seront réévalué à un moment donné au cours d’autres opérations sur l’instance de projet.Removing an import marks the project as dirty, which means that the project will be re-evaluated at some point during other operations on the project instance.
